    <p class="mt-2">Product manager, designer, or engineer? Stay in the loop with weekly notes and resources on <strong>maximizing</strong> your outcomes.</p>
    <form action="https://xyz.us11.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=6dc0c39e37a97ab5a03b51343&amp;id=5c2e4bb0d0" method="post" class="mt-6 w-full max-w-lg inline-flex flex-nowrap justify-center rounded-sm shadow">
        <input type="email" id="mce-EMAIL" name="EMAIL" placeholder="Type your email..." required class="flex-1 px-3 py-2 text-neutral-strong bg-neutral border border-r-0 border-neutral-strong focus:border-neutral-strong focus:outline-none focus:ring-0 rounded-none rounded-l-sm">
        <button type="submit" name="subscribe" class="flex-none px-4 py-2 font-medium text-neutral bg-neutral-strong border border-l-0 border-neutral-strong rounded-r-sm">
            Subscribe
        </button>
    </form>
    <p class="mt-4 text-caption text-neutral-medium">
        Every Sunday by <a href="https://helloraz.com" target="_blank" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-neutral-medium font-medium hover:text-neutral-strong">Raz Tirboaca</a>
